{"id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_Nzk4_0010","text":"但你的雙腳亦留在愛河","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["陪伴","愛","支持"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愛河","雙腳","留在"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,4,2,0,2,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","nei5","dik1","soeng1","goek3","jik6","lau4","zoi6","oi3","ho4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"雙腳","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"留在","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛河","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"對比過去的失落，強調對方始終陪伴在身邊，語氣充滿感激與愛意。"},"source":{"title":"三千零一夜","artists":["李克勤"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_798","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_Nzk4_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_Nzk4_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
